.TH "ntfs_clear_volume_flags" 9 "ntfs_clear_volume_flags" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ntfs_clear_volume_flags \- clear bits in the volume information flags
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ntfs_clear_volume_flags
.BI "(ntfs_volume *vol "  ","
.BI "VOLUME_FLAGS flags "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "vol" 12
ntfs volume on which to modify the flags
.IP "flags" 12
flags to clear on the volume
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Clear the bits in \fIflags\fP in the volume information flags on the volume \fIvol\fP.

Return 0 on success and -errno on error.
